{"tid":1448367,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［後續行動］鐵三角-遊行+deadline+十日大罷工","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:36.000Z","uid":100224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"50d08fb07363743f9fd190202a307ce382d01532","tid":1448367,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5svqTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5svqTe.jpg&h=2eb7d322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都好嬲今日果班狗做既所有野，所以呢個時候更加要動下腦後續點做！<br />\n<br />\n利申永遠唔割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>諗返6月果陣出現既一個concept</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>勇武完係需要和理非加deadline做support</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣我地先會有更強大既民意同動力去做接下來既革命！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">後續行動建議：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n短期內要搞一次和理非大遊行，遊完唔衝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n1. 抗爭兩個月後做一次民意統計<br />\n2. 設定deadline要求回應<br />\n3. Deadline唔回應升級全面大罷工十日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>原因：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 勇武既效能大幅降低，612衝同而家衝已經完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n2. 勇武再升級前，要用和理非最暴力去對抗，同時罷工果日唔可以衝，最多塞地鐵，將焦點放係罷工到<br />\n<br />\n3. 罷工前要宣言，遊行set deadline會係好方法<br />\n<br />\n4. 罷工要時間醞釀，所以遊行呢段時間會係一個好既時間<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">困難：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 不反對通知書唔會批，同樣會暴力清場，唔會和平得去邊<br />\n<br />\n2. 黑警如果扮示威者衝，個focus又會變左衝，而唔係罷工<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">解決方法（歡迎更多）</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 文宣以和理非為主調宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 口以相傳，提醒勇武人士忍忍手先，罷工完再郁手<br />\n<br />\n3. 將遊行擺係機場附近進行，令班狗唔可以暴力清場<br />\n<br />\n4. 未諗到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家覺得可行請推比民陣知，或者有乜不足一齊討論</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘班狗今日對我地做過既所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0dae595d16ce9047e9cc670e6d620cd9dfd57b49","tid":1448367,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3cc9bad84be8d25715d4ab997ade57f010432db","tid":1448367,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a750fbea2826f3334dc3ccdcfde90ad10dde7ccd","tid":1448367,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"418fc5e6b364a84bf9c03cc05a823ffd35f8eb16","tid":1448367,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae43abdd546b9a053beb55da43934b1c082e0efe","tid":1448367,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dae10e1a87887eff7b58290b89be9c60d1bdb7a9","tid":1448367,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}